            "body": "Thanks. I think you'll be hard pressed to find a repro where this matters, but yes this is just a typo from 4ef217e2 where we replaced a window handle that did have to be fetched from `M.wins` (which in a sense is less \"hard coded\" than the closure variables as is it is updated dynamically).",
